---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../index.css';
---

<Layout title="About Us - CozyPixels" description="Learn about the origins of CozyPixels, inspired by Sleepy Cats, curating the best 4K aesthetic wallpapers.">
  <main style="padding: 120px 24px 80px; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 720px; width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 1.7;">
      <h1 class="font-display" style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: #1e2444; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 850; letter-spacing: -0.04em;">About CozyPixels</h1>
      
      <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: #52607a; margin-bottom: 2rem;">CozyPixels was born out of a simple desire: to make digital spaces feel like home.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;">Our Story</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Heavily inspired by the serene aesthetic of Sleepy Cats, CozyPixels began as a personal curation project. We realized that the wallpapers we look at every day—whether on our phones, browsers, or dual-monitor PC setups—profoundly impact our mood and productivity.</p>
      
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Instead of endless scrolling through generic wallpaper sites, we wanted to build a definitive collection of high-resolution, minimalist, and "cozy" wallpapers. Specifically, we focus on beautifully crafted color palettes like <strong style="color: #2f365e;">Catppuccin</strong>, <strong style="color: #2f365e;">Nord</strong>, and <strong style="color: #2f365e;">One Dark</strong>.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;">More Than Just Wallpapers</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">What started as a simple gallery has evolved into a complete ecosystem. Today, CozyPixels offers a blazing-fast web experience, a native Windows Desktop Application for seamless local wallpaper management, and a Chrome Extension designed to boost productivity with integrated Pomodoro timers and lo-fi soundscapes.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #2f365e; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;">The Creator</h2>
      <p style="color: #626d86; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">CozyPixels is built and maintained by Nikhil Yadav (<a href="https://github.com/yadavnikhil03" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">@yadavnikhil03</a>). It is an open-source labor of love dedicated to the developer and design community.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
